noticing my ass.

19:46.233 --> 19:48.300
Hey, hey, hey, hey,
don't kill the messenger.

19:48.300 --> 19:49.600
It's the first law
of landscaping.

19:49.600 --> 19:51.667
If you trim down the tree,
the backyard looks bigger.

19:51.667 --> 19:53.800
Am I right?

19:53.800 --> 19:55.600
Damn you, Charlie Harper.

19:55.600 --> 19:58.133
What?
Tell the doctor
I changed my mind.

19:58.133 --> 19:59.333
What did I say?

19:59.333 --> 20:00.800
Where are you going?
Home.

20:00.800 --> 20:02.000
